[div class=p 
	[a class=intlink href=/Users/Profile/Baxter 
		"Baxter
	]a
	": It is not allowed to use a password to skip to the end, as explained in the 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=rules|href=/MovieRules#NoSkippingToTheEndWithAPassword)
	". There are conceivable scenarios where using a password is warranted, but these are very rare. When you want to make such a movie it is a good idea to discuss this on the forum first, or ask a judge about it. Furthermore, the (U) version of the game is the preferred version by default, a shorter title screen is specifically 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=listed|href=/MovieRules#UseTheCorrectVersion)
	" as a bad reason to use a different version. Rejecting this TAS.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The audience seems rather interested in a full TAS of this game, so hopefully we will see that some day.
